sq95Nqfi4lG","name":"Self-Repair Boost Buff","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"Once per activation, before attacking, pick one friendly unit within 12\", which gets Self-Repair Boost once (next time the effect would apply).","hasRating":false,"coreType":null,"targetType":1},{"id":"nstknew-_RL_","name":"Rending in Melee","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"This model gets Rending in melee.","hasRating":false,"coreType":5,"targetType":1},{"id":"YtzjP0K3sIAh","name":"Mobile Artillery","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"When this model uses a Hold action and shoots at enemies over 9\" away, it gets +1 to hit rolls. As long this model hasn't moved during the round, when enemy units shoot at it from over 9\" away, they get -2 to hit rolls.","hasRating":false,"coreType":null,"targetType":1},{"id":"8haZ36fXvnzn","name":"Stealth Aura","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"This model and its unit get Stealth.","hasRating":false,"coreType":null,"targetType":1},{"id":"L--qMjlm2g4Q","name":"Piercing Assault Aura","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"This model and its unit get Piercing Assault.","hasRating":false,"coreType":null,"targetType":1},{"id":"QMU04E_1bAVC","name":"No Retreat Aura","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"This model and its unit get No Retreat.","hasRating":false,"coreType":null,"targetType":1},{"id":"nNh98rpX_sZv","name":"Casting Buff","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"Once per activation, before attacking, pick one friendly model within 12\" with Caster, which gets +1 to casting rolls once (next time the effect would apply).","hasRating":false,"coreType":null,"targetType":1},{"id":"Ldhtmr4H8b6G","name":"Slow","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"Moves -2\" when using Advance, and -4” when using Rush/Charge.","hasRating":false,"coreType":1,"targetType":1},{"id":"17crjK7P6_w6","name":"AP","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"Targets get -X to Defense rolls when blocking hits.","hasRating":true,"coreType":1,"targetType":2},{"id":"6mJw5IdqSqNC","name":"Ambush","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"May be set aside before deployment. At the start of any round after the first, may be deployed anywhere over 9” away from enemy units. Players alternate in placing Ambush units, starting with the player that activates next. Units that deploy via Ambush can’t seize or contest objectives on the round they deploy.","hasRating":false,"coreType":1,"targetType":1},{"id":"xfXomZDK5SVX","name":"Reanimation","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"When a unit where all models have this rule is activated, roll as many dice as the max. number of models/wounds it could restore. For each 5+ you may restore one model/wound. Note that new models may only be restored if they can be placed in coherency with non-restored models.","hasRating":false,"coreType":null,"targetType":1},{"id":"TU7fkKrcAvop","name":"Protection Feat","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"Once per game, when this unit takes wounds and all its models have this rule, you may use this rule and roll one die per wound, and on a 5+ it is ignored.","hasRating":false,"coreType":null,"targetType":1},{"id":"H9E9PIWpGRdw","name":"Relentless","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"When this model shoots at enemies over 9\" away, unmodified results of 6 to hit deal 1 extra hit (only the original hit counts as a 6 for special rules).","hasRating":false,"coreType":1,"targetType":1},{"id":"8Ck9GAwUK824","name":"Indirect","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"Gets -1 to hit rolls when shooting after moving. May target enemies that are not in line of sight as if in line of sight, and ignores cover from sight obstructions.","hasRating":false,"coreType":1,"targetType":2},{"id":"QXyt-zV_bjpg","name":"Unstoppable","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"Ignores Regeneration, and ignores all negative modifiers to this weapon.","hasRating":false,"coreType":1,"targetType":2},{"id":"a0YtInGiUDd6","name":"Tough","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"This model must take X wounds before being killed. If a model with tough joins a unit without it, then it is removed last when the unit takes wounds. You must continue to put wounds on the tough model with most wounds in the unit until it is killed, before starting to put them on the next tough model (heroes must be assigned wounds last, even if already wounded).","hasRating":true,"coreType":1,"targetType":1},{"id":"ZqewrI-hqAYi","name":"Self-Repair Boost","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"If all models in this unit have Self-Repair, they ignore wounds on rolls of 5-6 from Self-Repair (instead of only on 6+).","hasRating":false,"coreType":null,"targetType":1},{"id":"cavWDboL4ubs","name":"Rending","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"Ignores Regeneration, and on unmodified results of 6 to hit, those hits get AP(+4).","hasRating":false,"coreType":1,"targetType":2},{"id":"9jyvRoBODD-O","name":"Stealth","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"When units where all models have this rule are shot from over 9\" away, enemy units get -1 to hit rolls.","hasRating":false,"coreType":1,"targetType":1},{"id":"DhLjIDRrWz6-","name":"Piercing Assault","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"This model gets AP(+1) when charging.","hasRating":false,"coreType":null,"targetType":1},{"id":"O2Cd7OibBBA5","name":"No Retreat","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"When a unit where most models have this rule fails a morale test that causes it to be Shaken or Routed, the test counts as passed instead. Then, roll as many dice as the number of wounds it would take to fully destroy it, and for each result of 1-3 the unit takes one wound, which can't be ignored.","hasRating":false,"coreType":null,"targetType":1},{"id":"47CAqf7ySlfc","name":"Caster","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"Gets X spell tokens at the start of each round, but can’t hold more than 6 tokens at once. At any point before attacking, spend as many tokens as the spell’s value to try casting one or more spells (only one try per spell). Roll one die, on 4+ resolve the effect on a target in line of sight. Models within 18” in line of sight of the caster’s unit may spend any number of spell tokens at the same time before rolling, to give the caster +1/-1 to the roll per token.","hasRating":true,"coreType":1,"targetType":1},{"id":"HmxkJq_My-Ub","name":"Rapid Advance","aliasedRuleId":null,"description":"This model moves +4\" when using Advance actions.","hasRating":false,"coreType":null,"targetType":1}],"forceOrgErrors":[]}